    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It runs but has significant mechanical issues that require immediate attention before reliable use. The exterior shows heavy wear with scratches, dents, and scuffs throughout. The interior is worn with visible damage to the seats and trim. Best suited for someone with mechanical skills or as a parts vehicle.",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project car or a parts vehicle? Here's your chance! We'll be straightforward with you: this car is in poor condition and will need significant work \u2014 there are noticeable mechanical issues and cosmetic wear throughout. That said, it's a great candidate for a dedicated DIY enthusiast or someone looking for an affordable restoration project. Come take a look and see the potential for yourself!",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly in poor condition, and the price reflects that reality. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 there are multiple deep scratches, noticeable dents, and areas where the paint has faded or peeled entirely. Some rust is visible along the lower panels and wheel wells. The interior is worn with torn upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and several non-functional features including a broken center console latch and damaged door trim. Mechanically, the car runs but requires attention \u2014 there is a noticeable rough idle, the check engine light is on, and the suspension feels loose over bumps. The tires have uneven wear and will likely need replacement soon. This listing is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project vehicle or someone looking for basic transportation with the understanding that repairs will be needed. No major hidden surprises \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we want to give you a clear and honest picture of what you're getting. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains most of its original luster with only minor surface scratches and a small scuff on the rear bumper that are consistent with normal everyday use. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing moderate wear on the driver's seat and some light fading on the dashboard trim, but nothing that detracts significantly from the driving experience. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts promptly, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are in good working order. We did have the brakes inspected recently and they have good life remaining. The tires have approximately 40% tread left and will likely need replacement within the next year or so. All in all, this is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been reasonably cared for and is ready for its next owner without any major surprises.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Here's a well-maintained vehicle that checks all the right boxes for the discerning buyer. This car presents beautifully inside and out \u2014 clean interior, solid mechanicals, and a road-ready stance that speaks to conscientious ownership. Routine maintenance has been kept up, and it drives with the confidence you'd expect from a car that's been genuinely cared for. No hidden surprises, no cutting corners \u2014 just a dependable, attractive vehicle priced to move. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself why this one won't last long on our lot.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! \ud83d\ude97 I'm excited to share this fantastic ride with you today! This beauty is in great shape and has been well cared for \u2014 you can tell the previous owner really loved it. She runs smoothly, the interior is clean and comfortable, and she's ready to hit the road for your next adventure. Sure, she's got a little character from years of use (what well-loved car doesn't?), but nothing that'll slow you down. I'm a straight shooter \u2014 what you see is what you get, and I think you're going to love what you see. Come take her for a spin and feel the difference yourself. Priced to move and ready for a new home. Don't miss out \u2014 deals like this don't last long!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Rolling out of our inventory is this rock-solid performer that's been living its best life on the open road. The powertrain delivers crisp throttle response with no hesitation across the RPM band \u2014 cold starts are immediate, idle is smooth, and highway cruising is effortless. The suspension geometry remains tight with no perceptible play in the steering rack, and the brake system bites confidently with excellent pedal feel front-to-rear. The drivetrain transfers power cleanly through all gear ranges with zero slippage or clunk. Cosmetically, the body panels carry the honest patina of a well-driven machine \u2014 minor surface wear consistent with active ownership, but structurally sound with no rust compromise or structural flex. Interior surfaces show use but remain fully functional across all controls, HVAC, and infotainment inputs. This is a mechanically competent, road-ready unit that a discerning driver can put straight into rotation without hesitation. Priced to reflect its genuine capability.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Solid daily driver. Runs strong, looks clean. No major issues. Ready to go today.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Meet your next great adventure companion \u2014 a spirited road warrior that's lived a full life and still has plenty of story left to tell. This beauty carries the confidence of a car that's been trusted mile after mile, with a personality that shows in every curve and contour. The interior wraps you in that perfect blend of familiarity and function, while the engine delivers the kind of reliable pull that makes every commute feel like a journey. She's not fresh off the showroom floor \u2014 she's better. She's broken in, character-rich, and ready to be yours. Whether you're chasing weekend escapes or navigating the daily grind, this car brings soul to every drive. Come see her in person and feel the difference between a car and a companion.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle is ready to impress the discerning buyer. Featuring a clean interior, solid mechanical foundation, and a presentation that reflects years of attentive ownership, this car offers dependable performance and everyday reliability. Minor cosmetic wear consistent with normal use only adds character \u2014 the fundamentals are sound. Ideal for drivers who want real value without compromise. Come see it in person and discover why it won't last long on our lot.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    }
  ],
